CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 18, 2005

[Cite as 04/18/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1782.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2004-1143. In re McCord.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by respondent of a motion for reinstatement. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED that the motion be, and hereby is, denied.
